@NODE INTRO
@TITLE "02 Introduction"
@{"  Main   " LINK MAIN}

               @{I}"You can run but not hide from an AMIGA."@{UI}

                           @{B}What Is TheBoss?@{UB}

  Aptly named TheBoss this system manager is optimized simplicity,
  speed, compactness, versatility, flexibility and very efficient
  memory utilitization. Configuration is quick and easy with a wide
  range of possible user customized configurations from the simple
  to the complex. Programs and applications run from a single button
  click.

  Choose the Workbench screen. Choose any screen. TheBoss happily
  runs any selected public screen. Or if none selected on its own
  screen.

  With button selections for drawers, programs and scripts, few
  software options are not supported. Build a directory tree with
  all associated programs and functions for each directory or
  drawer. None excluded. All programs and program types accepted.

  No messy icons, docks or menus. Just simple buttons that make
  your Amiga the amazing computer it truly is.


                           @{B}TheBoss features@{UB}

  * Completely user configurational. No additional utilities required.
  * Fully font sensitive GUI. Selectable screen and button fonts.
  * Complete OCS/ECS/AGA support. Selectable screen modes.
  * All functions on a single screen. No menus, icons or docks.
  * No separate interface required. Does not require MUI or Classact.
  * Fully asynchronous multitasking. Extremely system friendly. User
    compliant.
  * 16-color Workbench palette. Selectable foreground/background colors.
  * Efficient memory usage. All data dynamically allocated. Only small
    amount of memory required. Memory release back to pool on exit.
  * Selectable button types. Chose from Drawer, Executable and Script.
  * Allows an unlimited number of buttons. As few or as many as desired.
  * Useful operations like Add, Insert, Switch, Copy and Remove make
    configuration alterations quick and easy.
  * Separate Preferences for initial and continuing configuration.
  * All windows dragable and remembered on exit.
  * Completely user selectable button width from narrow to screen width.
  * 100% language localized. English and French supported. Other
    languages supported soon.
  * Small, fast optimized code. Code optimization continual process.
  * Extremely easy to use. Very user friendly.
  * Completely configurable to any user configuration. Imagination
    is the only limit.
  * Fully tested to be as "bug" free as "bug" free ever is.  
  * Complete support for registered and unregistered users.  
  * More exciting features in the future...

                             @{B}TheBoss is Shareware.@{UB} 

