@NODE SYSTEM
@TITLE "04 System Requirements"
@{"  Main   " LINK MAIN}

                      @{I}"100% AMIGA for the AMIGA."@{UI}

                          @{B}System Requirements@{UB}

  TheBoss requires OS 2.1+ ROMS. This is an absolute minimum requirement.
  Do not use TheBoss on systems with OS versions older than OS 2.1+.

  TheBoss requires that following library files to be present on your
  system Libs directory:

  1. ASL.library      (As part of the OS 2.1+ release)

  2. Diskfont.library (As part of the OS 2.1+ release)

  3. Locale.library   (As part of the OS 2.1+ release)

  TheBoss has been tested on Amigas 2000/3000/1200. TheBoss should
  perform admirably on any Amiga meeting the above minimum requirements. 

  If you encounter any exceptions, kindly contact the author immediately.
  Please state the nature of the failure along with a complete
  description of your system configuration. Any information given will 
  help to determine cause for correction.

  TheBoss is as free from" bugs" as possible. Your cooperation in reporting
  any abnormalities or aberrations will only result in further improvement.

@ENDNODE

